{
  "stem": "13251.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, there was always this hoping, anticipating that we'll-- we'll-- we'll finally meet-- meet-- meet our parents.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we saw that kind of fading, you know, as a possibility.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Well, we never really found out ever, exactly what happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was only from the relatives that we met in the United States that just acknowledged that they were taken from the ghetto one-- at one time, probably in the late, you know, the latter part of the-- of the war, out of the ghetto, into concentration camps, and never came out.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember-- not a whole lot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- in fact, that's the only letter I could remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there might have been a couple of others.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I guess the post in those days wasn't the greatest, you know, especially coming out of a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, if that came from, like, from a major city, Prague, even then, it was war time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, it's-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There might have been a couple of letters before that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know there-- there weren't a lot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eh, they probably-- what they said, you know, I hope you have your-- you know, you're both well, and that's about it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, what else?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I don't remember writing back ever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'll never remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Little kids couldn't even write.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I learned English at the age of six, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went in-- I went straight into first grade.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And before long, I guess I could write English.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- Did you get a good education over there?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In England, you get a great education, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--not that much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not-- we didn't really talk about that a whole lot.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
